name: Shiba Punkz
description: $SPUNK is the first native token of the DefiPunkz DAO ecosystem and the centerpiece digital asset behind the upcoming (Q4 2023) blockchain game "Shiba Punkz" running on its own side chain. DefiPunkz is a collaborative GameFi launchpad created to bridge competitive online gaming and Play-to-Earn utilizing blockchain, while simultaneously uniting communities in the DeFi space. Our debut FPS Battle Royal "Shiba Punkz" is a next-gen P2E title being built from the ground up on Unreal Engine V.
